##  How to Add Issues to the Board

1. Go to **Projects ‚Üí New Project ‚Üí Board (Kanban)**
2. Name it: `DevStations Roadmap` or `DevStations Volunteer Tasks`
3. Add the **columns** above
4. Use **‚ÄúAdd cards‚Äù ‚Üí Issues** to link your existing issues to the board
5. Volunteers can **drag issues** from To Do ‚Üí In Progress ‚Üí Done as they work

> Tip: You can also **filter cards by labels** (`good first issue`, `help wanted`) for easy sorting.

---

##  Optional Enhancements

* Use **milestones** if you want to group issues into sprints or feature sets
* Add **priority labels** (`high`, `medium`, `low`) so volunteers know what‚Äôs urgent
* Add **notes/cards** for ‚ÄúIdeas‚Äù or ‚ÄúFuture Features‚Äù

---

‚úÖ **Example Project Board Layout for DevStations**

```
DevStations Volunteer Tasks
------------------------------------
To Do
  - Add Dark Mode Toggle [frontend, help wanted]
  - Write README tutorial [documentation, good first issue]
  - Add unit tests for /api/posts [backend, help wanted]
  - Improve Navbar Responsiveness

In Progress
  - Fix navbar responsiveness [frontend, help wanted]

Review / QA
  - PR #12: Add post creation validation [backend, help wanted]

Done
  - Initial repo setup with Flask + React
```
### 1Ô∏è‚É£ Add Dark Mode Toggle (Frontend)
**Description:**
Implement a dark/light theme switch for the UI. Make sure it works across all pages and persists user preference.
**Label:** `help wanted`, `frontend`
### 2Ô∏è‚É£ Add Pagination for Posts (Frontend + Backend)
**Description:**
If there are many posts, display them in pages (10 per page). Implement both backend pagination in Flask and frontend display in React.
**Label:** `help wanted`, `frontend`, `backend`
### 3Ô∏è‚É£ Unit Tests for Backend API
Write pytest/unittest cases for `/api/posts` endpoints. Ensure edge cases like empty input, invalid data, and proper HTTP status codes are tested.
**Label:** `help wanted`, `backend`, `tests`
### 4Ô∏è‚É£ Profile Page for Users (Frontend + Backend)
**Description:**
Create a user profile page showing posts and basic info. Connect to backend API and handle routing.
**Label:** `help wanted`, `frontend`, `backend`
### 5Ô∏è‚É£ Improve Cloud Deployment Scripts
**Description:**
Update Docker / deployment configuration for multi-environment (GCP + Render). Add CI/CD support if possible.
**Label:** `help wanted`, `devops`, `cloud`
### 6Ô∏è‚É£ Improve UI Styling / Responsive Design
**Description:**
Make the UI fully responsive on mobile/tablet. Refactor CSS or React components for better layout.
**Label:** `help wanted`, `frontend`, `enhancement`
---

### 7Ô∏è‚É£ Add Form Validation for Posts

**Description:**
Validate input fields for creating posts (title, content). Show error messages on invalid submission.

**Label:** `help wanted`, `frontend`, `backend`

---

### 8Ô∏è‚É£ Write Tutorials / Documentation

**Description:**
Add step-by-step tutorials or expand README for running the app locally, API usage, or deployment guides.

**Label:** `help wanted`, `documentation`


## 1Ô∏è‚É£ Add a Dark Mode Toggle (Frontend)

